{"tid":2061153,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[消失的新聞］由聽日起12.6.2019 嘅新聞就會喺 RTHK 嘅網頁消失","createTime":"2020-06-12T07:41:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T10:21:32.000Z","uid":185251,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"a2db631e6e0ea31dd6933a92b35737c721785b1e","tid":2061153,"uid":185251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T07:41:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LOL1ygy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLOL1ygy.jpg&h=f9c330b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廢話唔多講，大家都知過去一年嘅新聞對將來編寫香港歷史有幾咁重要，能夠以中立角度報導事實嘅媒體更加係寥寥可數。香港電台作為公營機構，喺資源緊絀嘅情況下，仍然盡心盡力為香港人服務。但剛剛上去港台網頁就發現&rsquo;新聞重溫&lsquo; 只可以睇返最近一年嘅新聞。而家仲可以睇到舊年612 嘅新聞，但之前嘅已經睇唔返，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">換言之，聽日就唔可以再喺港台網頁重溫612嘅報導</span></strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n我唔知道嗰啲新聞已經消失喺呢個世上，定只係佢哋archive 咗無公開。如果係消失咗固然唔能夠接受，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但若果係後者，將來中共接收港台時，1984情節就會隨時發生，改寫歷史無難度。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n呢個post 唔係要攻擊港台，只係想推比多啲人知道，睇吓有無其他媒體或者議員跟進，又或者有無IT 巴絲可以喺事情解決之前有辦法backup啲報導。<br />\n  <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><em><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n&lsquo;Who controls the past controls the future. Who controls the present controls the past.&lsquo; &mdash; 1984 by George Orwell<br />\n</span></em></span></strong>"},{"pid":"a7fbb9da5cd53e530e018b3cde500e552fac94ea","tid":2061153,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T08:03:33.000Z","msg":"Backup"},{"pid":"6e0ab03d8d29a20cc7b202d2927ae68736a22741","tid":2061153,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T08:04:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7ded2